git status: what's going on?

UPLOADING
ZONE 1
1. git add: ZONE 2
2. git commit: ZONE 3
3. git push origin main

DOWNLOADING
1. git remote update
2. git pull origin main

BRANCHING
1. make sure you have DOWNLOADED everything
2. git branch tf/new_function
3. git checkout tf/new_function
4. actually do the coding
5. UPLOAD (when you're done)


